         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>The formula recall tombstones of Asia Minor rather than the local tradition, and it would be reasonable to suspect that the subjects may have been immigrants, 
               or the descendents of immigrants, perhaps under the schemas of Trajan and Hadrian to repopulate Cyrenaica after the Jewish revolt of C.E. 115.<!-- , see introduction--></p>
         </div>
         
